{"title":"祭罗瑞卿同志","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":8,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"祭罗瑞卿同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姚远方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"良师乘云去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜宿谁家？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太行麾下卒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哀哀泪如麻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗大聆教诲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延水论中华。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音容犹似昨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪气贯云霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逐鹿平津保，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鏖战在新沙。（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵前善鼓动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指挥若品茶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关山飞征衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎马度生涯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多谋复善断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"治军业绩嘉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无私方敢言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有胆能识假。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是非早判定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横眉斥秃鸦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身残志不残，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋勇斗鬼邪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征登新途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大树忽凋拔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千军尚易得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一将最难求。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辞世留重任，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后继有新芽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长歌当哭痛未定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍悲奋笔不尽话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一首诗成人亦苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海天心祭不需花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：新沙，指河北省的新保安和沙城，平津战役时，罗瑞卿同志参与指挥，在这一带全歼蒋军主力第三十五军，促进了北平的和平解放。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}